data.description: Recent $20,000 price reduction! A charming all-brick home nestled in the rural town of Orlinda, TN. Sitting on over half an acre of fully fenced land, offering both privacy and security. Inside, you'll find a cozy fireplace, custom shelving, and built-ins throughout, adding character and functionality to the space. The gravel driveway leads to a garage, providing convenient parking. Upstairs, a versatile bonus space awaits, perfect for entertaining, creating a home theater, or indulging in recreation. Step out onto the back deck or front porch and soak in the peacefulness of this quiet neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home!
